  "text": "where g is the sigmoid function. The derivation of equation 9 is provided in the Supplementary Material (Section 2). This coordinate ascent strategy is common in variational inference for conjugate exponential family distributions [CITATION_1] . We term this model RVAE-CVI (Coordinate ascent Variational Inference) in the rest of the text.",
